Steps to use this automation for single node:

1. Make sure you have latest copy of the code: use "git pull"

2. Edit "hosts" file & enter your "kubernetes-master" ip address

3. Edit all.yml under "kubeadm-automation/group-vars/all.yml" as follows
   Change "deployment_type: singlenode". Default is "deployment_type: singlenode"
   Note:  Do not edit this file if you wish to keep everything default.

4. Execute follwing script:
   ansible-playbook -i <path-of-repository/hosts> --private-key /root/.ssh/kubernetes.pem trigger.yml
   
5. Log location: /tmp/logs
